OL,5, Some residents living in social housing
OL,6, in Rochdale blighted by damp and mould 
OL,7, said they had been told they were      
OL,8, breathing too much.                    
OL,10,FThe group, who shared their stories at 
OL,11,Fa meeting at a local pub, all live in  
OL,12,Fproperties managed by Rochdale         
OL,13,FBoroughwide Housing (RBH).             
OL,15,FThe landlord was also responsible for  
OL,16,Fthe property where two-year-old Awaab  
OL,17,FIshak died from exposure to mould.     
OL,19,FRBH said it was working to carry out   
OL,20,Frepairs to affected homes.             
